<i>noun</i>: 비소설 [비ː소설], 논픽션 [] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비소설 [비ː소설]</dt><br>
<dd>nonfiction</dd><br>
<dd>꾸며 낸 이야기가 아닌, 사실을 바탕으로 쓴 문학 작품.</dd><br>
<dd>A piece of literary work based not on made-up stories but on facts.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>논픽션 []</dt><br>
<dd>nonfiction</dd><br>
<dd>꾸며 낸 것이 아닌 사실에 근거하여 쓴 이야기.</dd><br>
<dd>A story not based on fabrication, but based on reality.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>